### Create a new Business record
POST http://localhost:3000/business
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Acme Corp",
  "description": "Global provider of road runner deterrents",
  "phone": "+1234567890",
  "email": "info@acmecorp.com",
  "website": "https://www.acmecorp.com"
}

### Retrieve all Businesses
GET http://localhost:3000/business

### Retrieve a single Business by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/business/1

### Update an existing Business
PUT http://localhost:3000/business/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Acme Corp Updated",
  "description": "Leading innovator in cartoon contraptions",
  "phone": "+0987654321",
  "email": "support@acme-innovations.com",
  "website": "https://acme-innovations.com"
}

### Delete a Business
DELETE http://localhost:3000/business/1
